---
import heroBg from '../assets/images/hero-bg.png';
---

<section class="hero-section" style={`background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 85%), url(${heroBg.src});`}>
  <div class="container hero-container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>iPSテクノロジーで、<br />神経疾患創薬の“現在地”を<br class="sp-only" />押し広げる</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Time Biotechnologiesは、患者由来iPS細胞を用いた高度な疾患モデリングと<br class="pc-only" />
        スクリーニング基盤により、治療薬開発の時間を短縮し、新たな価値を創造します。
      </p>
      
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/pipeline" class="btn btn-primary">Pipelineを見る</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">お問い合わせ</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    padding: 10rem 0 8rem;
    min-height: 85vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }

  .hero-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.8rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--c-primary);
    text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--c-gray-800);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .sp-only { display: none; }
  .pc-only { display: inline; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }
    
    .sp-only { display: inline; }
    .pc-only { display: none; }
    
    .hero-sub {
        font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
